<br>
I certainly support the idea of smaller government, as most of you know by now.  However, I cannot continue to support tax cuts in the absence of corresponding spending cuts at this time as our deficit is just out of control.<br>
<br>
Ideally, I'd like to see tax cuts and spending cuts.  However, if we can't get the spending cuts through, I think we have to wait on the tax cuts.<br>
<br>
